ime":"2020-02-13T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"下體唔舒服呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:46:15.000Z","msg":"老母感到安慰"},{"pid":"47cdb08edfc1ff30e55ee7405a040f26b35b1af7","tid":1877903,"uid":123308,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:50:08.000Z","msg":"用葉劉超薄情趣口罩咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ikt9gcE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fikt9gcE.gif&h=b41e81f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KsdM2SE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsdM2SE.gif&h=45ff0966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dk6buxF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDk6buxF.gif&h=ca0670e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200213/LGJFMEL5UQ4JVZ24RB5PR7BR5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FLGJFMEL5UQ4JVZ24RB5PR7BR5Y%2F&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=bdc03531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FLGJFMEL5UQ4JVZ24RB5PR7BR5Y%2F&h=b54157c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200213/LGJFMEL5UQ4JVZ24RB5PR7BR5Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：誘阿公阿婆 葉劉派透視罩 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n透視口罩，禾真係見過！八方講緊咩？咪就係新民黨葉劉淑儀前日送出嘅超薄口罩。事緣葉太近日收到新民黨中委王聰德父子捐贈「一批來自日本的口罩」，「質素不錯」，會將呢批口罩派畀老人院公公婆婆。解人一罩之困，好事當然要公諸於fb。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葉劉個罩薄過蟬翼。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfb河蟹「日本口罩」<br />\n<br />\n可惜好多街坊拎完口罩之後都大表失望，皆因口罩呈半透明，猶如喱士，戴上面都隱隱透視膚色，好多網民質疑「薄到冇功能，戴三個都嫌薄」。所謂禍不單行，有網民發現葉劉呢盒綠色口罩，疑似唔係日本貨，而係淘寶價六蚊人仔50個，由產地湖北直送，快遞有貨。<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅形勢下，葉劉可能見勢色不對，噚日靜靜雞改咗fb個po，將「日本口罩」同「質量不錯」兩大承諾撤回，改稱「一批口罩」。有傳媒打畀葉劉問吓發生咗咩事，葉劉就話派畀街坊嗰陣有講明材質較薄，「唔嫌棄先好攞」，言下之意就係拎咗唔好怨。葉劉仲補充，香港各界缺罩，搵到靚貨如N95，會優先畀醫院，口罩「有好過冇」。有網民就話，唔係嫌唔嫌棄嘅問題，而係薄到咁，分分鐘害到老人家，好事變壞事！<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"8357925afe52c66028a856ada48a29789e57a241","tid":1877903,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c0fed715c1c0f35485b8b125c83118ddb2f688","tid":1877903,"uid":30647,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:52:49.000Z","msg":"立場D圖, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用粉紅加心, 重要係塊臉加兩個粉紅"},{"pid":"bb51becff66505618c932ce547e2ded4209bee31","tid":1877903,"uid":303805,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"呢排間間美術鬥痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8961d63b985451f493a7ebf51d123b75d9beea3","tid":1877903,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81c0fed715c1c0f35485b8b125c83118ddb2f688","tid":1877903,"uid":30647,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:52:49.000Z","msg":"立場D圖, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用粉紅加心, 重要係塊臉加兩個粉紅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"你唔講都無見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325542d01a3